- I know how to work it, Benjy!

1324
01:33:40,323 --> 01:33:43,074
I know how to work it.
Hello, down on the ground.

1325
01:33:43,242 --> 01:33:44,909
This is us in the air.

1326
01:33:45,077 --> 01:33:47,037
We're in this fella's plane.

1327
01:33:47,204 --> 01:33:48,872
He knocked himself out...

1328
01:33:49,040 --> 01:33:52,709
...because he drank a whole case
of bourbon and hit his head.

1329
01:33:52,877 --> 01:33:54,377
What do we do?

1330
01:33:54,545 --> 01:33:57,047
The switch, let go of the switch!

1331
01:33:57,214 --> 01:33:59,382
If you can,
give us your position.

1332
